    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 I2C bus — manages the HAL handle and device collection. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>One bus instance per I2C peripheral (I2C1, I2C2, etc.). Devices are created via <ref refid="classStmI2cBus_1a8a8333a7f2c46e1c89da0d80b19e1f79" kindref="member">CreateDevice()</ref> and accessed via <ref refid="classStmI2cBus_1a7d31764b7f52bfd6eaf6249d70231f5d" kindref="member">GetDevice()</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
